text: Derevnya Uchkhoza selkhoztekhnikuma () is a rural locality (a village) in Kushnarenkovsky Selsoviet, Kushnarenkovsky District, Bashkortostan, Russia. The population was 36 as of 2010. There is 1 street. == Geography == It is located 6 km from Kushnarenkovo. == References == Category:Rural localities in Kushnarenkovsky District
title: Derevnya Uchkhoza selkhoztekhnikuma
